          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀμυδίς</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἅμα</span>): Aeolic adv., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">at once.</span> —(1) of place,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">together, in a mass</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καθίζειν,
            κικλήσκειν</span>, etc., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πάντ᾽ ἀμυδίς, μ
            413</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 12.385</span></i>.—(2) of
          time, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">at once, immediately</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 23.217</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 14.305</span></i>;
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">at the same time</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            5.467</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
